      <title>据英国《金融时报》报道，英国钢铁公司所有者举行会谈以避免工厂关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/uk-british-steel-owner-held-talks-to-avert-plant-closures-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《金融时报》援引未具名政府和业内消息人士的话称，英国商务大臣乔纳森·雷诺兹已与英国钢铁公司的中国所有者举行会谈，以避免工厂关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/uk-british-steel-owner-held-talks-to-avert-plant-closures-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 14:53:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴里克落后于竞争对手，第二大矿业公司未能从黄金繁荣中获益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/barrick-falls-behind-rivals-as-no-2-miner-misses-boost-from-bullion-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，随着金价屡创新高，全球大多数顶级黄金矿商的股价都大幅上涨。但巴里克黄金公司 (Barrick Gold Corp.) 除外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/barrick-falls-behind-rivals-as-no-2-miner-misses-boost-from-bullion-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
