    <item>
      <title>交易员认为现在是 2016 年，而股市必须在 2024 年生存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/traders-think-it-s-2016-while-stock-market-has-to-live-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，一种似曾相识的感觉笼罩着华尔街，唐纳德·特朗普的胜选给股市带来了与他八年前胜选时类似的震动。小型股飙升，银行股大涨，标准普尔 500 指数创下了历史上最好的选举日表现和 12 个月来最强劲的一周表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/traders-think-it-s-2016-while-stock-market-has-to-live-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗因担心发电厂引发健康问题而暂停发电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/iran-targets-outages-amid-health-concerns-from-power-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据半官方的伊朗学生通讯社报道，伊朗将实施计划停电措施，以限制使用污染燃料的发电厂的电力生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/iran-targets-outages-amid-health-concerns-from-power-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 12:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>图斯克称希望在 2025 年保持波兰能源价格稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/tusk-says-wants-to-keep-polish-energy-prices-frozen-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克表示，波兰政府计划明年维持能源价格不变，并批评欧盟限制碳排放的计划对经济有害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/tusk-says-wants-to-keep-polish-energy-prices-frozen-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 11:30:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚在金砖国家扩张中的新角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-09/ethiopia-s-new-role-in-brics-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年早些时候，埃塞俄比亚加入了金砖国家集团，阿拉伯联合酋长国、伊朗和埃及也加入了该组织，加入了该组织现有成员国巴西、俄罗斯、印度、中国和南非。彭博社的海伦·尼亚姆布拉报道了这个撒哈拉以南非洲国家和东非最大经济体希望实现的目标。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-09/ethiopia-s-new-role-in-brics-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 11:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度电力金融公司拒绝向 Shapoorji 提供 24 亿美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/india-s-power-finance-turns-down-2-4-billion-debt-to-shapoorji</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度国营电力金融有限公司的一位高级官员表示，该公司已决定不向 Shapoorji Pallonji 集团提供贷款，这使得该基础设施集团再融资约 2000 亿卢比（24 亿美元）债务的计划受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/india-s-power-finance-turns-down-2-4-billion-debt-to-shapoorji</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 09:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国即使收到阿达尼付款仍面临电力供应减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/bangladesh-faces-reduced-power-supplies-even-after-adani-payment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国面临持续的电力短缺，即使已向印度一家发电厂支付了部分款项，但该发电厂因未付账单而削减了供电，停电风险仍然加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/bangladesh-faces-reduced-power-supplies-even-after-adani-payment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 09:05:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《华尔街日报》报道，俄罗斯考虑合并最大石油公司的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/russia-weighs-plan-to-merge-biggest-oil-companies-wsj-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，俄罗斯官员和企业高管已就将该国最大的几家石油公司合并为一家石油生产商进行了会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-09/russia-weighs-plan-to-merge-biggest-oil-companies-wsj-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 06:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
